text: George Kinek (January 13, 1929 – January 21, 1995) was an American football end. He played for the Chicago Cardinals in 1954. He died on January 21, 1995, in Salisbury Township, Pennsylvania at age 66. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:1995 deaths Category:American football ends Category:Tulane Green Wave football players Category:Chicago Cardinals players
